      "content": "i dont want to \"take things a step at a time\" anymore. every step just feels like i'm dragging myself through mud. i'm just so tired of the cycle. i keep thinking about how peaceful it would be if i didn't have to feel any of this. if i could just... stop. just completely stop feeling everything. i just want it to be over.",
